room_title: Escape room "Voodoo Queen" by Crack the Code in Flint
room_description: The esteemed voodoo queen Mystique Boudreaux has gone missing. It is rumored that she tried to make herself immortal, but something went wrong. It is said she is now in limbo, trapped between the living and the dead. A victim of her own spells, Madame Boudreaux needs your help to return to her famed New Orleans. It is your mission to enter her secret ritual room, decipher her spells, and open the portal to free her from the undead.
